# Files uploaded to EAS Build. Mirrors .gitignore semantics. Excludes content the
# native iOS/Android build never needs, to shrink the archive (was 439 MB).
#
# DO NOT ignore: assets/ (holds proto.zip + app icons/splash), src/, ios-certs/
# (local build credentials), supabase/, proto/ (kept for safety), or any app config.

# Marketing website + its heavy PNG/WEBP/MP4 sources — a separate static site, not the app.
web/

# Screenshots, QA captures, audit + design artifacts.
_media/
qc/
sim/
docs/

# Claude Code tooling. The skills symlink farm can break the EAS tarball; nothing here
# is part of the build.
.claude/

# Loose QA/marketing images dropped at the repo root (root-anchored so app assets are safe).
/*.jpeg
/*.jpg
/a1-*.jpeg
/qa-*.jpeg
/art4-final.png
/ob2-role.jpeg
